 "If e.g. BIR is in the list, then so should be BMR, MIR, and if those are there, then so should MRR")

                       (for ETAIL FS FACE SOURCE NEWFONTS on EXPANDED
                          do (SETQ FS (CAR ETAIL))
                             (SETQ FACE (fetch (FONTSPEC FSFACE) of FS))
